title: Private Talks

description:
Today on the show we opened up the phone lines to see what our listeners thought about a private school teacher teaching first graders about masturbation with the moral of the story being that some things should just be spoken about in private or not at all. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a 20 year only fans girl that suffered heart attack while attempting sexy strip tease while “dry scooping” (swallow spoonful of cinamon) and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee"
